Vunani Says It Expects to Report Annual Loss Per Share of as Much as $0.07

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-28T06:22:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/vunani-says-it-expects-to-report-annual-loss-per-share-of-as-much-as-0-07.html
Vunani Ltd. (VUN)  said it expects to post
a basic loss per share of between 2.1 South African cents and
4.8 cents for the 12 months through December.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
